      <title>JVM 基础原理 01：一文吃透 JVM 整体架构</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/posts/jvm%E5%9F%BA%E7%A1%80%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%8601%E4%B8%80%E6%96%87%E5%90%83%E9%80%8Fjvm%E6%95%B4%E4%BD%93%E6%9E%B6%E6%9E%84/</link>
